name: TYPO
description:
Homey Collection of Font Pairs & Typography with Free Google Fonts Library (inc. Figma)


Combinations of fonts and typography from unusual typefaces that you may not have seen. For those who are looking for something new and trying to deviate from the usual font sets.


The set will be filled with new variations in the future, but for now, I hope I helped you a little.
